Oh, thanks.

486
00:34:52,283 --> 00:34:54,547
Well,
this is it.

487
00:34:54,619 --> 00:34:57,452
It's, um...
It's impressive.
[Chuckles]

488
00:34:59,824 --> 00:35:01,849
