all this crap!

528
00:38:22,927 --> 00:38:24,861
[Clanking Tools]
[George]
I'm not done with that yet.

529
00:38:24,929 --> 00:38:27,989
Well, get it out...
Oh, Jesus!

530
00:38:28,066 --> 00:38:30,432
Relax.
Shit!
Where did it go?

531
00:38:30,501 --> 00:38:32,867
Where is it?
