fucking bit of difference.

544
00:39:27,659 --> 00:39:30,685
[Sighs]
I don't know
what happened to me.

545
00:39:34,666 --> 00:39:36,600
[Crying]
I mean...

546
00:39:36,668 --> 00:39:41,002
God, I was Miss Wichita,
for Christ's sake.

547
00:39:42,874 --> 00:39:44,808
Did I tell you that?

548
00:39:46,644 --> 00:39:52,378
