551
00:40:02,727 --> 00:40:06,686
And I thought it meant
I was gonna do something
important with my life,

552
00:40:06,764 --> 00:40:10,165
that it meant I was someone.

553
00:40:16,674 --> 00:40:20,303
You're someone to me.

554
00:40:29,220 --> 00:40:32,986
Are you gonna be
something else that
I have to survive?

555
00:40:34,592 --> 00:40:36,753
'Cause I'll tell you
the truth,

556
00:40:38,529 --> 00:40:41,225
I'm not up to it.

557
00:41:23,074 --> 00:41:25,406
So I get up on the stage,
in the center of the stage,
right?

558
00:41:25,476 --> 00:41:29,970
I had a big bouquet of flowers
and I had my foot out like this
and I say,

559
00:41:30,047 --> 00:41:35,110
