"I will devote my entire reign
as Miss Wichita...

560
00:41:35,186 --> 00:41:37,677
"to bringing an end
to world hunger...

561
00:41:37,755 --> 00:41:41,213
"and to the creation
of a peaceful Earth...

562
00:41:41,292 --> 00:41:44,090
[Chuckling Continues]
For every man, woman
and child."

563
00:41:44,162 --> 00:41:48,030
How long were you
gonna be Miss Wichita?
One year.

564
00:41:48,099 --> 00:41:51,535
Of course,
by the time I got through
opening new supermarkets,

565
00:41:51,602 --> 00:41:55,936
I only had a few weeks left
to work on hunger
and world peace.

566
00:41:56,007 --> 00:42:00,103
World peace. Right.
[Fake Laughing] I don't know
what I was thinking about.

567
00:42:01,312 --> 00:42:03,246
What about you, huh?

568
00:42:03,314 --> 00:42:05,441
What about me?

569
00:42:07,485 --> 00:42:10,784
What about you?
[Laughing]
[Laughing]

570
00:42:10,855 --> 00:42:13,483
Hey, baby, let me
tell you something.

571
00:42:13,558 --> 00:42:17,324
Let me get that
out of your hair.
Oh.

572
00:42:17,395 --> 00:42:20,296
Thank you.
