599
00:44:06,336 --> 00:44:09,328
Look, what is all this?

600
00:44:09,406 --> 00:44:14,639
What's the story
on this cancer stuff?

601
00:44:14,711 --> 00:44:18,613
You want to know?
You have to hire me back.
I got a ton of bills to pay.

602
00:44:20,384 --> 00:44:23,353
Fine. Fine.

603
00:44:23,420 --> 00:44:27,880
So, Donna just put in
these new cabinets...
stained the wood and all...

604
00:44:27,958 --> 00:44:29,983
when she gets a call
from somebody at PG&E...

605
00:44:30,060 --> 00:44:31,994
saying there's a freeway
gonna be built...

606
00:44:32,062 --> 00:44:34,895
and they want to buy her house
to put in an off-ramp
to the plant.

607
00:44:34,965 --> 00:44:37,729
Meanwhile, the husband's sick
with Hodgkin's.

608
00:44:37,801 --> 00:44:40,031
She's in and out of the hospital
with tumors,

609
00:44:40,103 --> 00:44:42,731
believing one thing
has nothing to do
with the other.

610
00:44:42,806 --> 00:44:45,036
Because PG&E told her
about the chromium?

611
00:44:45,108 --> 00:44:47,042
Get this.
They had a seminar.

612
00:44:47,110 --> 00:44:49,476
They invited
about 200 residents
from the area,

613
00:44:49,546 --> 00:44:51,480
had it at the plant
in this warehouse,

614
00:44:51,548 --> 00:44:54,711
