about chromium three
and how good it is for you...

615
00:44:54,785 --> 00:44:57,049
when all the time
they're using chromium six.

616
00:44:57,120 --> 00:45:02,524
[Beth Fussing]
T-T-That document
you found at the water board...

617
00:45:02,592 --> 00:45:07,427
the one that says
about the bad chromium...

618
00:45:07,497 --> 00:45:10,091
You didn't happen
to make a copy, did you?

619
00:45:10,167 --> 00:45:14,001
Of course I did.
Could I have
a look at it?

620
00:45:14,071 --> 00:45:18,269
I want a raise
and benefits,

621
00:45:18,342 --> 00:45:20,276
including dental.

622
00:45:20,344 --> 00:45:22,972
[Sighs]
Erin, this isn't the way
I do business.

623
00:45:23,046 --> 00:45:24,980
