[Sighs]

679
00:49:01,431 --> 00:49:03,729
Well, that one's
got absolutely nothing
to do with the other.

680
00:49:03,800 --> 00:49:06,462
Right.

681
00:49:06,536 --> 00:49:09,733
But PG&E paid
