00:49:46,376 --> 00:49:50,506
I'm saying the second
she pressed the "send"
button,

692
00:49:50,580 --> 00:49:54,107
PG&E's claim department...

693
00:49:54,184 --> 00:49:58,086
was on the phone to me
scheduling a meeting.

694
00:49:58,154 --> 00:50:00,622
So you think that we...
Let me do it...

695
00:50:00,690 --> 00:50:02,624
'cause you're
driving me nuts.
What?

696
00:50:02,692 --> 00:50:04,626
So you think
we scared them,
don't you?

697
00:50:04,694 --> 00:50:07,094
Well, they're
taking the trouble
to send someone.

698
00:50:07,163 --> 00:50:10,530
Sure as hell sounds like
they're sitting up
and taking notice.

699
00:50:25,282 --> 00:50:27,216
Mr. Foil?

700
00:50:29,886 --> 00:50:31,820
In the interest of putting this
whole thing to rest,

701
00:50:31,888 --> 00:50:36,416
